ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: 1. I find keeping in touch with family is as important now as it ever was.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 2. I often feel like I belong.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 3. I find I have many fulfilling roles in life.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 4. I don't feel I lack important ties with people outside of my family.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 5. I feel like I play a part in my community (neighborhood, town, city).
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 6. I don't feel a sense of shared values with the people I associate with.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 7. I would be missed if I moved far away.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 8. Having close friendships is an important part of my life.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 9. I feel like I spend enough time with people outside of my immediate family.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: 10. I feel like I contribute to the neighborliness where I live.
Notes: 1=Strongly Disagree; 2 =Moderately Disagree; 3 =Slightly Disagree; 4 =Slightly Agree, 5 =Moderately Agree; 6 =Strongly Agree
